channel.title: Spring '25 Week 15 :: CIS 526 Textbook
channel.description: Video Script Hello and welcome to the week 15 announcements video for CIS 526 and CC 515 in spring 2025. So here we are, we’re at the last real week of the semester before finals week. Hopefully everybody was able to get through the advanced topics tutorial. Hopefully it worked really well. It’s a lot of stuff that I wanted to add at the end of the class, but didn’t really fit anywhere else.
